Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.57,0:19:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在捕捉反應
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.63,0:19:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,優先確認位置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.33,0:19:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧？
